                    <span>This is the worst book ever written.  It has so many errors in it that one would wonder if they even edited it before they decided to publish it.  If you are smart you will not buy this book.  In addition to all the errors, it is extremely hard to follow.  There is almost NO text.  The "text" consists of tedious exercises that teach you very little if anything at all.  Each exercise contains very vague instructions and "Test Your Thinking" sections which rarely make any sense.<p>DO NOT BUY THIS BOOK! YOU WILL REGRET IT!</span>
                  
              
